name: myJOBman
overview:
myJOBman.com is a Job board connecting recruiters and Job seekers.

myJOBman.com is a job portal that offers a simple and a strong platform for interested and qualified jobseekers to search & apply for suitable positions and provide employers quality online-recruitment and employment-branding solutions at affordable price.

myJOBman.com was established with a mission to help people find right people and right jobs.

For organizations “ right people.

For jobseekers “ right jobs.
